  <brief_title>A Study of Ramucirumab (LY3009806) in Children With Refractory Solid Tumors</brief_title>
  <official_title>A Phase 1 Study Of Ramucirumab, a Human Monoclonal Antibody Against the Vascular Endothelial Growth Factor-2 (VEGFR-2) Receptor in Children With Refractory Solid Tumors, Including CNS Tumors</official_title>
